<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504075>
    bibo:endPage "174" ;
    bibo:journal "Raffles Bulletin of Zoology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2014-04-04" ;
    bibo:startPage "161" ;
    bibo:volume "62" ;
    dc:creator "Siriboon, Thanit; Sutcharit, Chirasak; Naggs, Fred; Rowson, Ben; Panha, Somsak" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the carnivorous snail genus Indoartemon Forcart, 1946 and a new genus Carinartemis from Thailand (Pulmonata: Streptaxidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504077>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504081> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504077>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Distribution map of Indoartemon spp. and Carinartemis spp. Indoartemon spp (white circle): (1) Indoartemon cingalensis (Benson, 1853); (2) Indoartemon layardianus (Benson, 1853); (3) Indoartemon glacilis (Collett, 1898); (4) Indoartemon eburneus (Pfeiffer, 1861); (5) Indoartemon fuchsianus (Gredler, 1881); (6) Indoartemon bidens (Möllendorff, 1883); (7) Indoartemon tridens (Möllendorff, 1898); (8) Indoartemon laevis (Blanford, 1899); (9) Indoartemon prestoni (Gude, 1903); and (10) Indoartemon medius, new species. Carinartemis spp. (black circle): (1) Carinartemis vesperus, new species; and (2) Carinartemis striatus, new species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4504077/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4504081>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Shells of Indoartemon spp: A, B, Indoartemon eburneus, (A) lectoype NHMUK 20120255, and (B) specimen CUMZ 5014, with apertural dentition, from Wat Tam Phalom, Loei; C, D, Indoartemon prestoni, (C) lectotype NHMUK 1922.8.29.5, and (D) specimen CUMZ 5015, with apertural dentition, from Wat Tam Ra-Khang, Si Samrong, Sukhothai. E–G, Indoartemon medius, new species, (E) holotype CUMZ 5016 with apertural dentition, (F) paratype CUMZ 5017, and (G) specimen CUMZ 5018 from Tam Lom-Tam Wang, Si Samrong, Sukhothai." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4504081/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

